ent-RMCCigarettePackSolRedsYellow-name = yellow sol reds
ent-RMCCigarettePackSolRedsYellow-desc = Claims to be all-natural and organic, with no additives. Not much better for your health than other brands, but they taste good and are highly addictive. This type seems to have a more mellow flavor.

ent-RMCCigarettePackSolRedsTurquoise-name = turquoise sol reds
ent-RMCCigarettePackSolRedsTurquoise-desc = Claims to be all-natural and organic, with no additives. Not much better for your health than other brands, but they taste good and are highly addictive.

ent-RMCCigarettePackEmeraldGreens-name = emerald greens
ent-RMCCigarettePackEmeraldGreens-desc = They remind you of a gross, tar-filled version of Ireland. These cheap cigarettes are Weston-Yamada's entry into the general market.

ent-RMCCigarettePackElectroGolds-name = Kierlan electro golds
ent-RMCCigarettePackElectroGolds-desc = Lovingly machine-rolled for YOUR pleasure. For when you want to look cool and the risk of a slow horrible death isn't really a factor.

ent-RMCCigarettePackLadyFingers-name = lady fingers
ent-RMCCigarettePackLadyFingers-desc = These intensely strong unfiltered menthol cigarettes don't seem very ladylike. They don't seem very fingerlike for that matter, either. Smoking may kill, but poor branding is almost as bad.

ent-RMCCigarettePackArcturianAce-name = arcturian ace
ent-RMCCigarettePackArcturianAce-desc = An entry level brand of cigarettes with a bright blue packaging. You're guessing these aren't really good for you, but it doesn't matter when it's Arcturian baby!

ent-RMCCigarettePackExecutiveSelect-name = executive select packet
ent-RMCCigarettePackExecutiveSelect-desc = These cigarettes are the height of luxury. They're smooth, they're cool, and they smell like victory...and cigarette smoke.

ent-RMCCigarettePackWeYaGold-name = We-Ya gold packet
ent-RMCCigarettePackWeYaGold-desc = Paving Better Worlds, and rolling better cigarettes. These fancy cigarettes are Weston-Yamada's entry into the premium tobacco market. Comes backed by a fierce legal team.

ent-RMCCigarettePackLuckySloths-name = lucky sloths packet
ent-RMCCigarettePackLuckySloths-desc = Lucky Sloths Means Fine Tobacco! 9/10 doctors agree on Lucky Sloths...as the leading cause of marine lung cancer.

ent-CMCigarettePackLuckySlothsMini-name = lucky sloths mini packet
ent-CMCigarettePackLuckySlothsMini-desc = These four-packs of Luckies come in every MRE. They're not as good as the Embassy Crowns found in some TSE MREs, but at least they're free.

ent-RMCCigarette-name = cigarette
ent-RMCCigarette-desc = An unfiltered roll of tobacco and nicotine. Smoking this releases even more tar and soot into your mouth.

ent-RMCCigaretteSpent-name = cigarette
ent-RMCCigaretteSpent-desc = An unfiltered roll of tobacco and nicotine. Smoking this releases even more tar and soot into your mouth.

